      <title>家庭能源费用即将降至两年来的最低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-30/household-energy-bills-about-to-fall-to-lowest-point-in-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 Ofgem 根据批发价格降低价格上限后，平均家庭能源费用将从下个月起降至两年来的最低点。]]></description>
